description:
Black Genesis
Injector

This four-pieced combo was born in 2012 at Cartagena, Spain. The sound of the band combines the aggressiveness and speed from Thrash Metal with the passion and melody of the most classic Heavy Metal.
 With no doubt,the essence of the band is their level of rapport; influenced by many different artists and musical styles related to their genre.
 New wave Thrash Metal by experienced musicians.. For fans of Sodom, Slayer, Exodus, Evile, etc.
